parse.title: List of countries by papaya production

text.*:
Countries by papaya production in 2016

This is a list of countries by papaya production in 2016, based on data from the Food and Agriculture Organization Corporate Statistical Database.[1] The total world production for papayas in 2016 was 13,050,749 metric tonnes. India was by far the largest producer, accounting for nearly 43.7% of global production.
